article.description: — Sean Houpt's 17 points helped William & Mary defeat American 75-56 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Houpt scores 17 in William & Mary's 75-56 win over American
article.linkText: Houpt scores 17 in William & Mary's 75-56 win over American
article.story: WILLIAMSBURG, Va. -- — Sean Houpt's 17 points helped William & Mary defeat American 75-56 on Thursday night. Houpt shot 4 for 7 (4 for 6 from 3-point range) and 5 of 6 from the free throw line for the Tribe (2-0). Gabe Dorsey scored 14 points and added nine rebounds. Trey Moss went 6 of 11 from the field to finish with 14 points. Jermaine Ballisager Webb led the way for the Eagles (0-2) with 12 points. Matt Mayock added eight points for American. NEXT UP William & Mary takes on George Washington on the road on Saturday, and American hosts Siena on Monday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
